ine a new star formation/AGN diagnostic\nwhich is consistent with all mid-infrared diagnostics already in use but has\nthe advantage that it can be applied to mid-infrared spectra with low signal to\nnoise or with limited spectral range. The 7 NMF components and code for\nclassification are made public on arxiv and are available at:\n\\url{https://github.com/pdh21/NMF_software/}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Oct 2013 14:55:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
