e rapid\nconformation changes. In part, these observations demonstrate the role that\nheat and pressure dissipation play on deformation characteristics of amorphous\npolymers, particularly for the strain hardening regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Oct 2013 15:04:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-03"}
